Append a FDR column to an InteRactome

Source: R/Main_functions.R
append_FDR.Rd

Append a FDR column to an InteRactome

append_FDR(res, df)

Arguments

res

an InteRactome
df

a data.frame containing (at least) columns 'bait', names', 'FDR' and 'conditions'

Value

an InteRactome

Examples

data("proteinGroups_Cbl")
#Run InteRact with default parameters
